quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  96,1,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Karimmi ni a Duuma So Ŋun nam yuli."
  96,2,"O namla ninsala ni ʒitalli."
  96,3,"Karimma! Yaha! A Duuma nnyɛ Ŋun tibgi."
  96,4,"Ŋuna n-nyɛ Ŋun baŋsi (ninsala) ni alkalimi."
  96,5,"O (Naawuni) baŋsila ninsala binshɛɣu o ni ʒi."
  96,6,"Haifa! Achiika! Ninsala nyɛla ŋun kpahiri yεɣiri tariga."
  96,7,"Domin o nyaya ka o mali buni zuɣu."
  96,8,"Achiika! Labbu shee nyɛla a Duuma (Naawuni) sani."
  96,9,"A nya ninvuɣu so ŋun mɔŋda."
  96,10,"Dabli (Annabi Muhammadu), o yi ti yɛn puhi jiŋli."
  96,11,"Di ni bɔŋɔ, O (dabli maa) yi bela dolsigu zuɣu?"
  96,12,"Bee ka o puhi (niriba) ni wuntia?"
  96,13,"Di ni bɔŋɔ, a nya ka o (Abu Jahli) yi labsi ʒiri niŋ (Annabi noli ni), ka lebi biri?"
  96,14,"Di ni bɔŋɔ, o bi mi ni Naawuni nyara (o ni niŋdi shɛli maa zaa)?"
  96,15,"Haifa! O (Abu Jahli) yi bi chɛ o ni niŋdi shɛli maa, achiika! Ti ni gbaagi o o gbetaa zuɣu."
  96,16,"ʒiri ni tuumbiɛrilana gbetaa."
  96,17,"Dinzuɣu, o bolimi o ʒisheenima (o sɔŋdiba)."
  96,18,"Ni baalim, Ti (Tinim’Naawuni) gba ni boli Zabaaniyanima (Bana n-nyɛ Malaaika shɛba ban guli ʒahannama buɣum)."
  96,19,"Haifa! (Yaa nyini Annabi)! Di doli o, ka zaŋ a gbiεɣu ŋmε tiŋgbani ni (A jεma shee), ka miri a Duuma Naawuni."
